142
00:09:09,600 --> 00:09:12,360
Did you remember that I take you
to enjoy the moonlight?

143
00:09:13,320 --> 00:09:14,160
Yeah.

144
00:09:21,200 --> 00:09:22,280
No matter when,

145
00:09:22,840 --> 00:09:24,080
