146
00:09:24,880 --> 00:09:26,040
You have to remember that.

147
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:27,640
Ok.

148
00:09:28,200 --> 00:09:28,960
Wait for me.

149
00:09:29,160 --> 00:09:30,320
